   632	class PerClassScorer:
   633	    """Scores ``(ground_truth, system_answer)`` with abstention, stratified by
   634	    class. Abstention against a positive query is a miss (0.0); answering a
   635	    negative query is a false positive (0.0). Correct abstention on a negative
   636	    query scores 1.0."""
